title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 8: Greg Carlwood From Higherside Chats
description:
Thank you for tuning into another amazing episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. On this very special episode of Tin Foil Hat my good friend Ryan Davis joins me in studio to cohost as we welcome the amazing Greg Carlwood from The Higherside Chats. On this episode we discuss....
1) Greg's Higherside Chats Podcast
2) David Seaman
3) Ancient Civilizations
